Don't bug out! Cicada season is approaching in many states, so @marascampo and I did a quick Q&A with entomologist, Mike Deutsch ⬇️ 

➡️ How often do cicadas appear? 

➡️ How long are cicadas around for?

➡️ Are cicadas dangerous? 

➡️ Why do cicadas make so much noise!?

➡️ Is there anything I can do to repel cicadas? 

For more on this topic, plus travel + safety tips from @thepointsguy, be sure to watch #TheDrOzShow tomorrow. 
.
.

We’ve got a ton of August babies in my family. Today is my sister Seval’s birthday, and it also happens to be my son-in-law John’s birthday. 
 
Seval, thank you for bringing joy to our mom. I love seeing you dance together. 

And John, you are like another sibling in the family. We love your insightful wisdom, powerful personality, and passionate love for all of us, especially Daphne. You are a spectacular father to our grandchildren (and an excellent sports partner). 
 
Happy birthday, Seval and John!
